SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE SOCIETY WAS INCORPORATED IN 1937 UNDER THE ILLINOIS GENERAL CORPORATION LAW TO OPERATE EXCLUSIVELY FOR CHARITABLE, EDUCATIONAL, SCIENTIFIC AND LITERARY PURPOSES WITHIN THE MEANING OF SECTION 501(C)(3) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE OF 1954. THE INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE HAS DETERMINED THE SOCIETY IS EXEMPT FROM FEDERAL INCOME TAX. HOWEVER, THE SOCIETY MAY BE SUBJECT TO FEDERAL AND STATE TAX ON UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME. THERE WAS NO TAXABLE NET INCOME FROM UNRELATED ACTIVITIES FOR 2023 AND 2022.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 7A
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: IN THE EVENT OF A CONTESTED ELECTION OF SOCIETY OFFICERS, THE ELECTIONS COMMITTEE (A PRESIDENTIAL APPOINTEE) SHALL CAUSE TO BE PREPARED AND DISTRIBUTED TO THE SOCIETY MEMBERS OFFICIAL BALLOT FORMS UPON WHICH SHALL APPEAR THE NAMES OF ALL CANDIDATES, THE OFFICES FOR WHICH THEY HAVE BEEN NOMINATED AND FULL INSTRUCTIONS FOR USE AND RETURN OF THE BALLOTS. CANDIDATES NOMINATED BY PETITION SHALL BE SO INDICATED.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE TREASURER REVIEWS THE RETURN THEN SENDS APPROVAL AND SIGNS THE RETURN. THE TREASURER REPORTS ON THE RETURN TO THE BOARD AND THE BOARD IS PROVIDED A COPY UPON REQUEST.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE EXECUTIVE VICE PRESIDENT PERFORMS AN EVALUATION OF THE STAFF EMPLOYEES EACH YEAR AND MAKES RECOMMENDATIONS REGARDING SALARY WHICH IS INCLUDED IN THE ANNUAL BUDGET. THE RECOMMENDATION IS APPROVED BY THE FINANCE COMMITTEE AND THEN GOES TO THE ENTIRE BOARD FOR FINAL APPROVAL. SALARIES ARE NOT ESTABLISHED BY AN INDEPENDENT OR THIRD PARTY ENTITY.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION'S FINANCE COMMITTEE OVERSEES THE ANNUAL AUDIT.
